#: data/io.otsaloma.gaupol.appdata.xml.in:7
msgid "Editor for text-based subtitles"
msgstr "基于文本的字幕编辑器"

#: data/io.otsaloma.gaupol.appdata.xml.in:9
msgid ""
"Gaupol is an editor for text-based subtitle files. It supports multiple "
"subtitle file formats and provides means of creating subtitles, editing "
"texts and timing subtitles to match video."
msgstr "Gaupol 是一个编辑基于文本的字幕编辑器。它支持多种字幕文件格式，并提供创建字幕、编辑文本和调整字幕时间轴以匹配视频等功能。"

